high_descs: Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right, go forward a bit, turn right at the table
Pick up the lettuce on the table
Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the fridge
Put the lettuce into the fridge, wait, take the lettuce from the fridge
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the table
Put the lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Cool a lettuce, put it on the table

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the counter, then turn right and walk up to the wall, after that turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the table.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the head of lettuce then close the door.
Turn around and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the white table.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the table.

high_descs: Turn to the white table to your left.
Pick up the head of lettuce, on the left side of the white table.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator, across from you.
Place the head of lettuce in the refrigerator, on the second shelf, to the right of the wine glass, wait a moment for the head of lettuce to chill, then remove the lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to the table on your right.
Place the head of lettuce back on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the table.
